Package org.zaproxy.zap.utils

Class HarUtils

java.lang.Object
org.zaproxy.zap.utils.HarUtils
@Deprecated(forRemoval=true, since="2.16.0") public final class HarUtils extends Object
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
(2.16.0) Use/rely on exim add-on.
Utility class to parse/create HTTP Archives (HAR) and do conversions between HAR Java classes and HttpMessages (request and response).
Since:
2.3.0
